Sentencas: Subsolidus equilibria in air in the RuO2-CeO2 and RuO2-Y2O3-CeO2 systems were studied with the aim of obtaining information on possible interactions between the Y2Ru2O7-based cathode and the CeO2-based solid electrolyte in solid oxide fuel cells (SOFC).
Titulo: Subsolidus phase equilibria in the RuO2-Y2O3-CeO2 system

Sentencas: In the RuO2-CeO2 system, no binary compound and no solid solubility were detected.
Titulo: Subsolidus phase equilibria in the RuO2-Y2O3-CeO2 system

Sentencas: In the RuO2-Y2O3-CeO2 system, no ternary compound was found.
Titulo: Subsolidus phase equilibria in the RuO2-Y2O3-CeO2 system

Sentencas: The tie line is between Y2Ru2O7 and CeO2.
Titulo: Subsolidus phase equilibria in the RuO2-Y2O3-CeO2 system
